					<td>
						<p>
							B&aacute;o c&aacute;o d&aacute;nh gi&aacute; doi song cua nguoi ngh&egrave;o v&agrave; nguoi l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng an luong cua Bo Ke hoach v&agrave; Dau tu cho biet, khoang 1,6 trieu c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n lao dong trong 260 khu c&ocirc;ng nghiep v&agrave; 15 khu kinh te dang phai doi mat voi nhieu kh&oacute; khan, thieu thon, tien luong kh&ocirc;ng du trang trai cho nhu cau cuoc song.</p>
						<p>
							B&aacute;o c&aacute;o n&agrave;y cung cho thay thu nhap cua c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n tai c&aacute;c khu c&ocirc;ng nghiep chi dat muc trung b&igrave;nh l&agrave; 2 trieu dong/th&aacute;ng, chi bang 68% so voi muc thu nhap trung b&igrave;nh cua c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n ca nuoc n&oacute;i chung. So tien n&agrave;y bao gom c&aacute;c khoan phu cap nhu tien di lai, tien tang ca, tien thu&ecirc; nh&agrave;&hellip;</p>
						<p>
							Theo Bo Ke hoach v&agrave; Dau tu, muc thu nhap cua nguoi ngh&egrave;o tang b&igrave;nh qu&acirc;n 10-20% trong khi gi&aacute; ca h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a dich vu lai tang 30-50%. Nguoi thu nhap thap o th&agrave;nh thi phai d&ugrave;ng hau het to&agrave;n bo thu nhap cua m&igrave;nh cho viec mua luong thuc, thuc pham, dien, nuoc, gas&hellip; den muc hau nhu kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n c&oacute; the d&agrave;nh dum duoc. Nhieu nguoi d&atilde; chap nhan song thieu thon.</p>
