			<p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 16px; padding: 5px 0px; text-align: justify;">
				Buoi toa d&agrave;m &quot;Part-time kh&ocirc;ng phai v&igrave; tien&quot; do B&aacute;o SVVN to chuc moi d&acirc;y d&atilde; cho biet l&yacute; do v&igrave; sao ho lai c&oacute; dam m&ecirc; d&oacute;.</p>
			<p style="margin: 0px; line-height: 16px; padding: 5px 0px; text-align: justify;">
				Ng&ocirc; Chi L&ecirc; (SN 1987) l&agrave; mot guong mat tre ti&ecirc;u bieu cho su tu tin, nang dong. C&ocirc; tung di l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m nhieu noi khi c&ograve;n l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n. C&ocirc; cuu sinh vi&ecirc;n DH Ngoai thuong n&agrave;y hien dang l&agrave;m viec tai Dai su qu&aacute;n Brazil. De c&oacute; duoc vi tr&iacute; l&agrave;m tot voi muc luong hien xap xi 1.000USD nhu hien nay, Chi L&ecirc; d&atilde; phai mat nhieu c&ocirc;ng suc, thoi gian de l&agrave;m viec cho Ph&aacute;i do&agrave;n Uy ban (UB) Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u tai VN m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng nhan duoc mot dong tien c&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o.<br />
				&nbsp;<br />
				Chi L&ecirc; ke: &ldquo;Hoi c&ograve;n l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n nam cuoi, t&ocirc;i d&atilde; manh dan gui ho so sang ph&aacute;i do&agrave;n xin thuc tap. Viec xin thuc tap v&agrave;o d&acirc;y het suc kh&oacute; khan. T&ocirc;i d&atilde; cho c&acirc;u tra loi rat l&acirc;u nhung van ki&ecirc;n tr&igrave;. Cho hon 3 th&aacute;ng moi c&oacute; duoc su dong &yacute; cua Ph&aacute;i do&agrave;n UB Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u. V&agrave;o d&acirc;y, t&ocirc;i duoc ph&acirc;n ve ban Thuong mai voi c&aacute;c viec nhu viet th&ocirc;ng c&aacute;o b&aacute;o ch&iacute; ve c&aacute;c hoat dong kinh te, thuong mai song phuong, soan thao c&aacute;c b&agrave;i ph&aacute;t bieu... Dieu kh&oacute; khan l&agrave; tat ca deu bang tieng Anh. Tieng Anh l&uacute;c n&oacute;i kh&aacute;c nhieu so voi van pham trong c&aacute;c van ban n&ecirc;n thoi gian dau t&ocirc;i gap nhieu kh&oacute; khan&rdquo;.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br />
				<br />
				Nhung dan dan sau khi duoc nhung nguoi di truoc chi bao, Chi L&ecirc; d&atilde; quen voi c&ocirc;ng viec.<br />
				&nbsp;<br />
				&ldquo;Nhung kien thuc bo &iacute;ch trong thoi gian l&agrave;m tai Ph&aacute;i do&agrave;n UB Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u gi&uacute;p t&ocirc;i tr&uacute;ng tuyen v&agrave;o Dai su qu&aacute;n Brazil trong ky tuyen dung day kh&oacute; khan&rdquo; - Chi L&ecirc; t&acirc;m su. Truoc d&oacute;, Chi L&ecirc; cung d&atilde; cong t&aacute;c viet b&agrave;i cho B&aacute;o SVVN, mot thoi gian l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m o D&agrave;i Truyen h&igrave;nh VN.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br />
				<br />
				Nguyen Hai H&agrave; - mot ban tre nang dong kh&aacute;c cung l&agrave; h&igrave;nh anh ti&ecirc;u bieu cho &yacute; ch&iacute; vuon l&ecirc;n, muon khang dinh m&igrave;nh. C&ocirc; sinh vi&ecirc;n DH Kinh te quoc d&acirc;n sau nhieu nam l&agrave;m viec trong c&aacute;c m&ocirc;i truong kh&aacute;c nhau hien dang l&agrave;m viec tai Viet Nam Airlines o ph&ograve;ng thuong mai dien tu. Nhung c&ocirc;ng viec tung l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m cua c&ocirc; g&aacute;i tre n&agrave;y l&ecirc;n den con so 10 nhu l&agrave;m tu van cho SITC, l&agrave;m Promotion Girl cho Happident, tu van vi&ecirc;n my pham, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n so&aacute;t v&eacute; trong rap chieu phim, tham gia c&aacute;c hoat dong t&igrave;nh nguyen...<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br />
				<br />
				Hai H&agrave; t&acirc;m su: &ldquo;Dieu quan trong voi m&igrave;nh khi di l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m l&agrave; de c&oacute; th&ecirc;m kinh nghiem v&agrave; nhung moi quan he. C&oacute; nhieu moi quan he se gi&uacute;p m&igrave;nh rat nhieu sau n&agrave;y. C&aacute;c ban sinh vi&ecirc;n n&ecirc;n dat ra cho m&igrave;nh nhu cau rang t&ocirc;i muon c&oacute; viec l&agrave;m. Su th&ocirc;i th&uacute;c d&oacute; se gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c ban t&igrave;m duoc viec v&agrave; som truong th&agrave;nh hon&rdquo;.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br />
				<br />
				Cung voi suy nghi kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n thiet hon, c&aacute;c ban tre trong nh&oacute;m Hanoikids lai mat nhieu thoi gian de l&agrave;m tour guide (huong dan vi&ecirc;n du lich) kh&ocirc;ng c&ocirc;ng cho c&aacute;c vi kh&aacute;ch nuoc ngo&agrave;i. Da so c&aacute;c ban deu l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n dang hoc tai H&agrave; Noi. Ban Viet - th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n cua nh&oacute;m cho biet: &ldquo;Tham gia hoat dong n&agrave;y gi&uacute;p ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; su trao doi van h&oacute;a voi kh&aacute;ch nuoc ngo&agrave;i, gi&uacute;p ho hieu hon ve H&agrave; Noi, dong thoi cung gi&uacute;p kha nang tieng Anh cua ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i tien bo hon&rdquo;.<br />
				<br />
				Moi nguoi mot l&yacute; do, nhung tat ca deu c&oacute; c&aacute;i nh&igrave;n ve tuong lai voi mong muon, nhung g&igrave; m&igrave;nh d&atilde; l&agrave;m kh&ocirc;ng phai l&agrave; v&ocirc; &iacute;ch.</p>
